{"tid":2479244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印尼發現武肺病毒新變種「Eek」","createTime":"2021-04-07T16:27:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T16:43:15.000Z","uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ad258d4cfb674fcc4632d01cb29da220ee6d5ce1","tid":2479244,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T16:27:43.000Z","msg":"印尼發現武肺病毒新變種「Eek」<br />\nIndonesia reports coronavirus case with &quot;Eek&quot; mutation<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-indonesia-mutation-idUSKBN2BT1FV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-health-coronavirus-indonesia-mutation-idUSKBN2BT1FV&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYS9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=fee8cbf1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-health-coronavirus-indonesia-mutation-idUSKBN2BT1FV&h=670daff0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-health-coronavirus-indonesia-mutation-idUSKBN2BT1FV</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXCTxJFTFNhucZfAEPiFHDrgWqaGsH1gAbYekAvZJ2shq?filename=Xy1vmwa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXy1vmwa.png&h=34917c23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據路透社4月6日報道，印度尼西亞報告了首例中共病毒新變種的感染病例，該變種病毒以其更易傳播和能降低疫苗保護性而聞名。<br />\n<br />\n此種新變種含有在南非和巴西首次發現的變種中發現的E484K突變。<br />\n<br />\n它被一些科學家戲稱為Eek，因為它明顯能躲早前中共病毒感染者產生的自然免疫力，並能減少現有疫苗提供的保護。<br />\n<br />\n之前日本也發現了這種E484K變種病毒，並且該國相關研究機構剛剛出爐了一份研究報告。該報告稱其有三大特性：<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">第一，能夠躲避免疫，現有疫苗可能對其無效；<br />\n第二，已經感染過中共病毒的人易於再次感染；<br />\n第三，感染力可能較強。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"c879a27784accc8ec1bb6b0c9a335ad7f516b0f2","tid":2479244,"uid":90392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T16:28:57.000Z","msg":"你話唔係支那投毒, <br />\n我真係唔撚信。<br />\n<br />\n等睇英美歐都有呢隻野。"},{"pid":"b0aa94bfc21b5d5c57dc31725453f79dc9820717","tid":2479244,"uid":152705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T16:36:23.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 ... 即係遲早都會中再加每年要不斷打疫苗。"},{"pid":"25a3f50267c4d943f27291e3da68b3bca5fde83b","tid":2479244,"uid":267680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T16:40:06.000Z","msg":"係咪即系分批中招最有效<br />\n愈後生愈安心"},{"pid":"d4c236e2797c34915828bb0065ec7156c4315e2d","tid":2479244,"uid":34517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T16:41:03.000Z","msg":"永續肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"559ee709139fcfe5a7dc6463d09f4d56039bbc36","tid":2479244,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T16:43:15.000Z","msg":"不如開返個國際機構幫啲病毒改花名<br />\n就好似D颱風咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}